Hirose Y, Saijou E, Sugano Y, Takeshita F, Nishimura S, Nonaka H, Chen YR (Chern EY), Sekine K, Kido T, Nakamura T, Kato S, Kanke T, Nakamura K, Nagai R, Ochiya T, Miyajima A. Inhibition of Stabilin-2 elevates circulating hyaluronic acid levels and prevents tumor metastasis. Proc Natl Acad Sci U S A. 2012; 109(11): 4263-8. (SCI)
Chen YR (Chern EY), Sekine K, Nakamura K, Yanai H, Tanaka M, Miyajima A. Y-box binding protein-1 down-regulates expression of carbamoyl phosphate synthetase-I by suppressing CCAAT enhancer-binding protein-alpha function in mice. Gastroenterology. 2009; 137(1): 330-40. (SCI)
Sekine K, Chen YR (Chern EY), Kojima N, Ogata K, Fukamizu A, Miyajima A. Foxo1 links insulin signaling to C/EBPα and regulates gluconeogenesis during liver development. The EMBO journal. 2007; 26(15): 3607-15. (SCI)
Huang CL, Chen YR (Chern EY), Liu WH. Production of androstenones from phytosterol by mutants of Mycobacterium sp. Enzyme and microbial technology. 2006; 39(2): 296-300. (SCI)
Chen YR (Chern EY), Huang HH, Cheng YF, Tang TY, Liu WH. Expression of a cholesterol oxidase gene from Arthrobacter simplex in Escherichia coli and Pichia pastoris. Enzyme and microbial technology. 2006; 39(4): 854-60. (SCI)











「這樣唸大學才不後悔」，陳彥榮著。2012年 4月。 平安出版社。ISBN：9789578038226。











宮島篤、陳彥榮 (2010) 利用人類誘導性全能幹細胞分化至第八凝血因子分泌細胞技術 (申請中)





















幹細胞，人類醫學難題終極曙光 - 每日頭條每日頭條幹細胞，人類醫學難題終極曙光2017-01-25 由 煥生匯 發表於 科學
